  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, non-randomized, controlled study to investigate the clinical outcome of surgery
      using the Harmonic knife vs the HF knife in patients requiring abdominoplastic surgery or
      body lift (Lockwood)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study is to measure amount of seroma in each interventional arm.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
